                                      </span>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="py-3 text-gray-600 font-normal">
                                        Mot de passe
                                    </td>
                                    <td class="py-3 text-gray-800 font-normal">
                                        <a href="javascript:void(0)"
